{"title":"JavaScript —— DOM & BOM","date":"2019-11-13T00:32:06.496Z","thumbnail":"https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/11/13/M8h6t1.md.jpg","link":"2019/11/13/DOM","tags":["浏览器","面试"],"categories":["Programming"],"updated":"2019-12-24T02:23:35.767Z","content":"<p>DOM，Document Object Model，即文档对象模型</p>\n<p>BOM，Browser Object Model，即浏览器对象模型</p>\n<h2 id=\"property形式和attribute的区别\">property形式和attribute的区别<a href=\"2019/11/13/DOM#property形式和attribute的区别\"></a></h2><ul>\n<li>property修改的是对象属性，不会提现在html结构中；</li>\n<li>attribute修改html属性，会改变html结构</li>\n</ul>\n<p>两者都会引起DOM的重新渲染。尽量使用前者。</p>\n<h2 id=\"DOM性能\">DOM性能<a href=\"2019/11/13/DOM#DOM性能\"></a></h2><ul>\n<li><p>DOM操作非常的’昂贵’，尽量避免DOM操作</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>对DOM查询做缓存</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> pList = <span class=\"built_in\">document</span>.querySelectorAll(<span class=\"string\">'p'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> length = pList.length</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>将频繁操作改为一次性操作</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> list = <span class=\"built_in\">document</span>.getElementById(<span class=\"string\">'list'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">let</span> frag = <span class=\"built_in\">document</span>.createDocumentFragment()</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; i &lt; <span class=\"number\">10</span>; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> li = <span class=\"built_in\">document</span>.createElement(<span class=\"string\">'li'</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">  li.innerHTML = i</span><br><span class=\"line\">  frag.appendChild(li)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">list.appendChild(frag)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"如何识别浏览器类型\">如何识别浏览器类型<a href=\"2019/11/13/DOM#如何识别浏览器类型\"></a></h2>  <figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> ua = navigator.userAgent</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">const</span> isChrome = ua.indexOf(<span class=\"string\">'Chrome'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"拆解URL的各部分\">拆解URL的各部分<a href=\"2019/11/13/DOM#拆解URL的各部分\"></a></h2>  <figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 假设当前url为： https://coding.imooc.com/lesson/115.html&amp;a=100#mid=30378</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(location.protocol)  <span class=\"comment\">// 'https:'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(location.host)      <span class=\"comment\">// 'coding.imooc.com'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(location.pathname)  <span class=\"comment\">// '/lesson/115.html'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(location.search)    <span class=\"comment\">// '?a=100'</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">console</span>.log(location.hash)      <span class=\"comment\">// '#mid=30378'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n","prev":{"title":"JavaScript —— 事件","link":"2019/11/13/event"},"next":{"title":"JavaScript —— 异步","link":"2019/11/12/asynchronous"},"plink":"http://allenxz.github.io/2019/11/13/DOM/","toc":[{"title":"property形式和attribute的区别","id":"property形式和attribute的区别","index":"1"},{"title":"DOM性能","id":"DOM性能","index":"2"},{"title":"如何识别浏览器类型","id":"如何识别浏览器类型","index":"3"},{"title":"拆解URL的各部分","id":"拆解URL的各部分","index":"4"}]}